flowchart TD
    C[Channel: Telegram / Web / Voice] --> A[Adapter]
    A -->|audio| STT[STT service faster-whisper]
    STT --> E[Unified JSON Envelope]
    A -->|text| E
    E --> AUTH[Auth: profile role/department]
    AUTH --> CL[LLM Classifier -> list of actions]
    CL --> R{Router per action}
    R -->|rag_query| RAG[Qdrant search + access filter -> answer with source]
    R -->|about| ABT[Introspect actions/channels/collections for this role]
    R -->|action chat| ACT[Validate -> call product API now]
    R -->|action confirm| CNF[Ok/Cancel card, park in Redis -> API on Ok]
    R -->|action link| LNK[Return deep-link, sensitive data]
    R -->|unknown| UNK[Add to 'could not' + reason]
    RAG --> AGG[Aggregator: one response]
    ABT --> AGG
    ACT --> AGG
    CNF --> AGG
    LNK --> AGG
    UNK --> AGG
    AGG --> OUT[Response back to the same channel]
